{"title_page": "List of The Dumping Ground characters", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2016}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''The Dumping Ground'' characters}}\nThis is a list of characters that were introduced in [[CBBC]]'s ''[[The Dumping Ground]]''. The series is based on [[The Story of Tracy Beaker]] by [[Jacqueline Wilson]]. It has aired since 2013 and is currently airing the seventh series. The series follows ''[[The Story of Tracy Beaker (TV series)|The Story of Tracy Beaker]]'' that ran for five series from 2002 to 2005, and ''[[Tracy Beaker Returns]]'' that ran for three series from 2010 to 2012.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ok.co.uk/books/1090870/jacqueline-wilson-writing-tracy-beaker-sequel-bbc-cbbc-dani-harmer|title=Jacqueline Wilson is bringing out a sequel to her The Story of Tracy Beaker book|work=Evening Standard|last=Flint|first=Hanna|date=4 June 2017|accessdate=23 October 2017}}</ref> Connor Byrne has played the role of [[#Mike Milligan|Mike Milligan]] for all three programmes.\n\n==Cast==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"1\" | Actor\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"1\" | Character\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 1)|Series 1]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 2)|Series 2]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 3)|Series 3]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 4)|Series 4]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 5)|Series 5]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 6)|Series 6]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 7)|Series 7]]\n! scop:8%;\" |\n[[The Dumping Ground (series 8)|Series 8]]\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Connor|Byrne}}\n| {{sortname|Mike|Milligan|Mike Milligan (character)}}\n| colspan=\"7\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Amy-Leigh|Hickman}}\n| {{sortname|Carmen|Howle}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Mia|McKenna Bruce}}\n| {{sortname|Tee|Taylor}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Joe Maw\n| {{sortname|Johnny|Taylor|List of Tracy Beaker Returns characters#Johnny Taylor}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{n/a}}\n| colspan=1 {{cGuest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Philip Graham Scott\n| {{sortname|Harry|Jones|List of Tracy Beaker series characters#Harry Jones}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Christopher John Slater\n| {{sortname|Frank|Matthews|Frank Matthews (Tracy Beaker)}}\n| colspan=2 {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{n/a}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Kay|Purcell}}\n| {{sortname|Gina|Conway}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"7\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Jessica|Revell}}\n| {{sortname|Elektra|Perkins}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{n/a}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Daniel|Pearson|Daniel Pearson (actor)}}\n| {{sortname|Rick|Barber}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Miles Butler-Hughton\n| {{sortname|Tyler|Lewis}}\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | {{sort name|Kia|Pegg}}\n| {{sortname|Jody|Jackson}}\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Jessie Williams\n| {{sortname|Lily|Kettle}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{n/a}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Leanne Dustan\n| {{sortname|Faith|Davis}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Sarah Rayson\n| {{sortname|Floss|Guppy}}\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Reece Buttery\n| {{sortname|Mo|Michaels}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cMain}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n| scope