lden Compass (video game)|The Golden Compass]]'' || Various characters || Grouped under Actor || <ref>{{cite video game | title=''[[The Golden Compass (video game)|The Golden Compass]]'' |  developer=[[Shiny Entertainment]] | scene=Closing credits, The Golden Compass Voice Cast, Actor | accessdate=June 19, 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2007|08|21|format=y}} || ''[[BioShock]]'' || [[List of Characters in Bioshock|Dr. Grossman]] || Grouped under Actors || <!-- voice chasers --><ref name=\"wormhole riders\"/><ref>{{cite video game | title=[[BioShock]] | developer=[[2K Boston]], [[2K Australia]] | publisher=[[2K Games]] | scene=Closing credits, 3:55 in, Actors }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2008|10|14|format=y}} || ''[[Dead Space (2008 video game)|Dead Space]]'' || [[Dead Space (2008 video game)#Plot|Captain Benjamin Mathius]] || || <ref name=\"wormhole riders\"/><ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2010|02|09|format=y}} || ''[[BioShock 2]]'' || [[List of characters in the BioShock series#Dr. Grossman|Dr. Grossman]] || || <ref name=\"wormhole riders\"/><ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|04|16|format=y}} || ''[[Injustice: Gods Among Us]]'' || [[Ares (DC Comics)|Ares]], [[Deathstroke]] || Grouped under Voice Talent, English || <!-- voice chasers --><ref name=\"injustice credits\">{{cite video game | title=''[[Injustice: Gods Among Us]]'' | developer=[[NetherRealm Studios]] | publisher=[[Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment]] | scene=Closing credits, 4:10 in, Voice Talent, English }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2017|07|18|format=y}} || ''[[Star Trek Online]]'' || [[Martok]] || Missions: \"Brushfire\", \"Scylla and Charybdis\" || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arcgames.com/en/games/star-trek-online/news/detail/10552414-j.g.-hertzler-joins-the-cast-of-star-trek-online|title=J.G. Hertzler Joins the Cast of Star Trek Online - Star Trek Online|author=|date=|website=arcgames.com|accessdate=December 3, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em|refs=\n<ref name=\"btva\">{{cite web|url=